title: Lumino Health Virtual Care
description:
Your health is important. Lumino Health Virtual Care, provided by Dialogue is here to help.

Access one of Canada’s largest virtual care team of doctors, nurses, nurse practitioners and other care professionals at your fingertips. Get personalized care, within minutes. You can connect by chat, audio or video.

With Lumino Health Virtual Care you can:
• Chat with a health-care provider through secure video
• Get help with prescriptions
• Connect with mental health specialists
• Speak with other health care professionals (e.g. nutritionists) for a fee.
• Add your eligible dependents (they have access to Lumino Health Virtual Care too!)

Lumino Health Virtual Care from Sun Life is provided by Dialogue
